{"word":"βασιλεύω","slug":"βασιλεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βασιλεύω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:βασιλεύς\">βασιλεύς</a></el>] <b><i>be king, rule</i> <a href='B:610 6:15'>1 Ti 6:15</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> simple <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <i>over/of</i> <b><a href='B:470 2:22'>Mt 2:22</a>;</b> also <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a></el> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:730 5:10'>Rv 5:10</a>,</b> or <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ acc.\">acc.</a> <b><a href='B:490 1:33'>Lk 1:33</a>.</b> In imagery <b><a href='B:520 5:14'>Ro 5:14</a>; <a href='B:520 5:21'>5:21ab</a>; <a href='B:520 6:12'>6:12</a>.—</b>In the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ aor.\">aor.</a> <el>β.</el> = <b><i>become king</i> <a href='B:530 4:8'>1 Cor 4:8</a>; <a href='B:730 11:17'>Rv 11:17</a>; <a href='B:730 19:6'>19:6</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βασιλεύς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βασιλικός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}